# Wireshark captures (optional - only if they contain sensitive data)
# Uncomment if you don't want to commit PCAP files:
# *.pcap
# *.pcapng

# Documentation build artifacts
docs/_build/
*.pdf

# MySQL dumps with actual data (keep schema, not data)
*_data_dump.sql

# Session receipts (may contain sensitive info)
*_receipt.json
receipts/

# Jupyter notebooks checkpoints
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# ========================================
# What TO COMMIT:
# ========================================
# ✓ Source code (.py files)
# ✓ README.md
# ✓ requirements.txt
# ✓ .env.example (template without real values)
# ✓ scripts/ (certificate generation scripts)
# ✓ Schema files (structure only, no data)
# ✓ Documentation
# ✓ Test scripts
# ✓ Screenshots (sanitized, no real passwords/keys)
